headline: Is It Too Late To Consider United Rentals (URI) After A Strong Multi Year Share Price Run
summary: If you are wondering whether United Rentals is still good value after a strong run, this article will walk through what the current price might be implying and how that lines up with several valuation checks. The stock most recently closed at US$892.10, with returns of 9.2% over 7 days, 11.9% over 30 days, 5.6% year to date, 31.3% over 1 year, 141.5% over 3 years and 251.4% over 5 years.
